        "body": "Contribute a \"Hello World\" implementation for a programming language that is NOT already present in the 'find here!!' directory of this repository.\n\n## Steps:\n- Identify a language missing from 'find here!!'.\n- Add a new folder named with that language.\n- Create the standard 'Hello World' code file for that language.\n- Inside the folder, also add a README.md with a brief explanation of the language and how to run your code.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria:\n- Language must not already exist in the repo.\n- Includes both source code and README.md.\n- The code prints 'Hello, World!' when run.\n- Follows repo guidelines for naming and format.",
